(Oh, KsLaw, Hysteria is hiding in a vent above the main bridge console, so I 
doubt you could 'look down' at her^_^ And yea Yanshosh, Hysteria is the 
original CF tech 'bot)

Hysteria:

Hysteria's internal computer alerted her to the approaching Alliance 'bots. 
When they entered the bridge she had the lockdown in effect and no computer 
was left exposed. After that was done she typed in a few more commands and 
targeted Unitron and Firestarter with several flamethowers per 'bot. They 
emerged from beneath retractable floor boards beside the entrance to the 
bridge.

A few moments later they fired a powerful burst of fire at the two invading 
'bots. She had rerouted some additional power to them in order to get her 
point across. She wanted them out... now. This may be Kluster's ship, but 
she was it's tech 'bot, and she wasn't going to let it fall into enemy 
hands.
